{"tid":1369381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉細良只係一個智囊 請大家做好分析","createTime":"2019-07-26T16:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T18:44:41.000Z","uid":46763,"like":170,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"8338d47d138d14bd1c392b1c0700731ab91c8c98","tid":1369381,"uid":46763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:33:35.000Z","msg":"我見到好多人捧神<br />\n好多人又反佢<br />\n<br />\n屌你 宗旨係咩 冇大台+不割席<br />\n<br />\n細良 曾經係政府工作 對政府運作十分熟悉<br />\n佢既意見好有參考價值<br />\n<br />\n但細良成日講 佢未必係岩 佢無意主導運動<br />\n佢都好信連登仔能力<br />\n連登仔自己思考啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔使標題黨<br />\n<br />\n我都好鍾意聽細良講<br />\n但聽完都要自己諗一諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58be36d352b903d76273a23f8f4b138fa4addb55","tid":1369381,"uid":103363,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8338d47d138d14bd1c392b1c0700731ab91c8c98","tid":1369381,"uid":46763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:33:35.000Z","msg":"我見到好多人捧神<br />\n好多人又反佢<br />\n<br />\n屌你 宗旨係咩 冇大台+不割席<br />\n<br />\n細良 曾經係政府工作 對政府運作十分熟悉<br />\n佢既意見好有參考價值<br />\n<br />\n但細良成日講 佢未必係岩 佢無意主導運動<br />\n佢都好信連登仔能力<br />\n連登仔自己思考啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔使標題黨<br />\n<br />\n我都好鍾意聽細良講<br />\n但聽完都要自己諗一諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:36:24.000Z","msg":"樓主個名咁鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但應該係聽完自己再諗，尤其佢用嘅例子同資料，自己再check 番啱定唔啱"},{"pid":"b4a6b30a5ca7776ff6f33274122d181985182631","tid":1369381,"uid":260037,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:41:52.000Z","msg":"推 只作參考 不盲從"},{"pid":"9b280effc0b4a19dca08b7df959c038379039f7c","tid":1369381,"uid":192988,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:42:29.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n<br />\n推<br />\n<br />\n利申，鍾意聽城寨，亦支持獨立思考"},{"pid":"a79f2e8171d57bd617ef205810a3bcf32b5b10f6",